title: ASW Restaurant v1.0
description:
The guys from Allstar Weekend have an appetite for rock n' roll and fine mexican cuisine! Help Zach, Cameron and Mike satisfy their insatiable hunger for nachos, burritos and tacos, but watch out for those hot peppers!

The fun never stops because the more food you eat, the more points you get! With help from all the various soda power-ups, you're sure to be chowing down on the highest scores!

Features:

- Starring Allstar Weekend!
- Tons of upgrades and power-ups to keep the fun going!
- Fun, addictive, never-ending gameplay!
- Unlock facts, pictures, music & more!
- Earn GameChange every time you play to redeem for real life prizes!
